t </strong>to keep reaching for their dreams.\r\n\r\nI can\'t wait to start working with YOU and help you acheive your dreams!\r\n\r\n</div>','Meet Clare','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision-v1','','','2012-10-12 01:07:09','2012-10-12 01:07:09','',10,'http://clarityinyourlife.com/success-coaching/10-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(10,2,'2013-06-11 13:01:12','2013-06-11 13:01:12','<a href=\"http://clarityinyourlife.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Clare_Standing_Pink.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-482\" alt=\"Clare_Standing_Pink\" src=\"http://clarityinyourlife.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Clare_Standing_Pink-199x300.jpg\" width=\"199\" height=\"300\" /></a><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><a><span style=\"color: #000000;\">I love what I do!</span></a></span>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><a><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Seeing clients grow in confidence gives me a completebuzz!\r\n</span></a>I came into the Coaching Profession after receiving coaching myself when I desperately needed a new career path. Because I had personally experienced just how much coaching transformed my life and well being, I decided to encourage and support others to take a risk and be happy  and to find a new and brighter direction in their lives.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">My company name <strong>Clarity in Your Life</strong> illustrates my approach  what you see is what you get! All very straightforward: My clients develop a much clearer idea of where theyre going when we work together.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I believe that as a Coach I should walk the walk as they say, so</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I set up a business in Training and Coaching in the UK at the start of the recession (2007) Crazy times but was very successful.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I was then in my mid 50s. Scary and incredibly exciting step forward.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Emigrated toAustralia in 2011 to be with my son and little family. One of my BEST decisions ever!</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I have developed a range of clients here initially as a self-employed Leadership and Management Trainer, with coaching clients: have a look at the <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a title=\"Success Stories\" href=\"http://clarityinyourlife.com/success-stories/\" target=\"_blank\">Success Stories</a></span></strong> to see what my clients say about our work together.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">This is all down to coaching  taking decisive action  getting organised I just lovethe energy and satisfaction in thisprocess!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">My life is a Work In Progress  and always will be.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Listen to my <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http://clarityinyourlife.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/01_Dreamy_Days.mp3\"><span style=\"color: #000000; text-decoration: underline;\">Radio Interview</span></a> </span></strong>to hear more of my story</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">*</span></span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">More workshops are coming soon.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Available to deliver</span></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">One to one Business and Leadership coaching  specifically for women Managers</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Group Coaching</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Coaching Workshops on Personal Development</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Public Speaking</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>','Meet Clare','','publish','open','closed','','about','','','2014-02-13 12:46:33','2014-02-13 01:46:33','',0,'http://clarityinyourlife.com/',0,'page','',0),(202,2,'2011-03-01 01:31:00','2011-03-01 01:31:00','','logo-60x60','','inherit','open','open','','logo-60x60','','','2011-03-01 01:31:00','2011-03-01 01:31:00','',0,'http://clarityinyourlife.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/logo-60x60.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(24,2,'2010-08-21 06:50:55','2010-08-21 06:50:55','','iStock_000005533011XSmall','','inherit','open','open','','istock_000005533011xsmall','','','2010-08-21 06:50:55','2010-08-21 06:50:55','',0,'http://clarityinyourlife.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/iStock_000005533011XSmall.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(27,2,'2010-08-21 07:02:38','2010-08-21 07:02:38','Portrait of a couple of businesspeople, in the middle of a cheerful talk.','Business partners','','inherit','open','open','','business-partners','','','2010-08-21 07:02:38','2010-08-21 07:02:38','',0,'http://clarityinyourlife.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/iStock_000004645784XSmall.jpg',0,'attachment','