at\'s me on there!\r\nCONTACT us by filling in the box on this page  - and receive a complimentsry copy of my SPECIAL REPORT\r\n\r\n\r\nHowever you choose to begin, taking the first step is <strong>saying YES to all things you desire!</strong>, \r\n\r\n<strong>Ask...Believe....Receive</strong>\r\n\r\nLooking forward to connecting with you soon!\r\n\r\n<strong>Clare Coffield</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 10px;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 10px;\"></div>','Home','','inherit','open','open','','188-revision-v1','','','2013-06-23 09:30:53','2013-06-23 09:30:53','',188,'http://clarityinyourlife.com/success-coaching/188-revision-12/',0,'revision','',0),(201,2,'2011-02-28 15:20:56','2011-02-28 15:20:56','','promotion','','inherit','open','open','','promotion','','','2011-02-28 15:20:56','2011-02-28 15:20:56','',110,'http://clarityinyourlife.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/promotion.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(244,2,'2011-11-16 02:19:00','2011-11-16 02:19:00','','logo','','inherit','open','open','','logo','','','2011-11-16 02:19:00','2011-11-16 02:19:00','',0,'http://clarityinyourlife.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/logo.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(273,2,'2013-06-11 13:00:55','2013-06-11 13:00:55','<strong>After Clares coaching you are left feeling good about yourself and really know that life can change for the better.</strong>\r\nS.W., Manager Engineering Company\r\n\r\n<strong> I came to find clarity and guidance and I am leaving excited, inspired and ready to take action towards achieving my goals</strong>\r\nLP, Local Authority Manager\r\n\r\n<strong>With Clares support and encouragement I achieved what I initially felt was far beyond my reach.</strong>\r\nAL, Manager, Holistic Centre.\r\n\r\n<strong>Clare has such a positive effect on my confidence levels that I come away, my bag of tools refilled once again, ready to tackle my next project.</strong>\r\nJ-LS, MD, Lindy Jazz Dance Company\r\n\r\n<strong>Before the workshop I was unsure what coaching was and whether it was for me. The session was really informative, fun and motivating and I learned a lot.</strong>\r\nCH, Business Solutions Manager, Natwest Bank\r\n\r\n<strong>I loved Clare\'s positive energy, enthusiasm and support through my coaching sessions. Clare was easy to get a rapport with and I felt really comfortable with her. Thanks so much. </strong>\r\nS HL\r\n\r\n<strong>I just wanted to thank you for the inspiring session we had last week when you did the guided visualization. I felt so good and I saw myself so relaxed and in peace. Everything I visualized happened in my life a few days after the session. I feel happy, empowered, inspired and ready to accomplish a ton of things.  Thank you Clare.</strong>\r\nC D\r\n\r\n<strong>I have had several coaching sessions with Clare to assist me in relation to my work as a Retail Manager. With her help I was able to identify but correct and grow key development issues with my staff. The coaching she has provided on an individual basis has given valuable insight and helped to recognise where I can improve myself and my staff. The skills and concepts I learned will be invaluable for the rest of my career.</strong>\r\nK B\r\n\r\n<strong>I absolutely love my coaching sessions with Clare.  I have not worked with a coach before so didn\'t know what to expect. I have been inspired to make change and appreciate coming away from each session with simple, easy steps - which I have designed - to make things happen for me.\r\n Having three young children I thought my life situation would be to mundane for coaching however Clare is able to walk me through what I can do to take control of where I want to be. She is very motivational, a great listener and is really helping me to make changes which are ongoing.</strong>\r\nO B\r\n\r\n<strong>Extremely helpful sessions.  It has been great to have the time to discuss my issues and work on actions. I have found Clare to be a skilled listener, intuitive and wise.  I trust her professionalism and have felt very comfortable. This has been a very good experience and I leave feeling inspired to change some previous thinking and behaviours. I am excited to get on with it.\"\r\nG M\r\n\r\nI\'m so glad I got the opportunity to meet Clare through a friend.  I have had a considerable amount of life challenges in the last 14 months. These have placed an enormous amount of stress in my life, taking its toll on my health and wellbeing. Since working with Clare she has helped enormously to work through a whole maze of issues and get some clarity and direction back into my life.\"</strong>\r\nNT','Success Stories','','publish','open','open','','success-stories','','','2013-09-06 02:29:56','2013-09-06 02:29:56','',0,'http://clarityinyourlife.com/?page_id=273',0,'page','',0),(398,2,'2013-06-11 02:24:02','2013-06-11 02:24:02','After Clares coaching you are left feeling good about yourself and really know that life can change for the better.S.W., Manager Engineering Company\r\n\r\n I came to find clarity and guidance and I am leaving excited, inspired and ready to take action towards achieving my goalsLorraine Pattison, Local Authority Manager\r\n\r\n With Clares support and encouragement I achieved what I initially felt was far beyond my reach.Ann Lockey, Manager, Holistic Centre.\r\n\r\nClare has such a positive effect on my confidence levels that I come away, my bag of tools refilled once again, ready to tackle my next project.Joo-Lee Stock, MD, Lindy Jazz Dance Company\r\n\r\nBefore the workshop I was unsure what coaching was and whether it was for me.  The session was really informative, fun and motivating and I learned a lot.Caroline Harper, Business Solutions Manager, Natwest Bank\r\n','Success Stories','','inherit','open','open','','273-revision-v1','','','2013-06-11 02:24:02','2013-06-11