ge.</span></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #3366ff; font-size: medium;\">Take the second step</span> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">and choose to invest a small admin fee of $7.97 to receive a copy of my Special Report(coming soon)</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600; font-size: medium;\">For Women Managers who would rather be somewhere else or doing something different.</span></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff; font-size: medium;\">Take the third step</span> <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">and claim your <span style=\"font-size: medium;\">free 30 minute coaching session</span> with</span> <span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Clare Coffield<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">(details in the Special Report)</span></span></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Looking forward to connecting with you soon</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">All the best</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://clarityinyourlife.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Clare_Blue.jpg\"><img src=\"http://clarityinyourlife.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Clare_Blue-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Clare_Blue\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-481\" /></a> \r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Clare Coffield</span></strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 10px;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>','Home','','inherit','open','open','','188-revision-v1','','','2014-02-02 11:49:13','2014-02-02 11:49:13','',188,'http://clarityinyourlife.com/success-coaching/188-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(487,2,'2014-02-08 09:45:42','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<!--  Hot Tip: Please do not D